capability.name: documents saved in the Xcode 8 format

fragment.string:
Start by setting a goal to be reached between 10 to 40 and set the number of rounds between 1 to 10 that the player has to reach that goal.
After setting the desired constraints, press the “Play” button.
You can roll the dice by clicking on the “Roll” button.
Scores will be calculated individually for Player 1 and Player 2 for each round.
When 1 appears on both of the dice for either or both players, then that player automatically wins.
When two of the dice of any or both players have magic combinations, then +3 is added to the score of that player or both players.
When 2,2 or 3,3 or 4,4 or 5,5 appears on both of the dice for either or both players, then +5 is added to the score of that player or both players.
When a player reaches the goal in or within the number of rounds then that player wins.
If both players reach the goal in or within the number of rounds then it will be tie.
You can start a new game after each game is won or lost.
You can restart the game anytime.
